Package: WaterDetection
Title: Water Detection for Dam level control (or lakes, bodies of water etc) using pre-processed Sentinel-2 imagery
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Pedro", "Fernandes", , "pedro.pires.fernandes@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
Description: Several functions that take composite Sentinel-2 imagery (with 10 bands) and run an algorythm that detects water in a shapefile based on a combination of RGB and NDVI values. 
    Exports pixel data as .CSV and builds time series graphs.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
